These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, banana, plum, kiwi
1. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
2. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | pineapple | banana | plum | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, almond-milk, milk
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea | sprite | milk | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, writing, photography, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | collecting | photography | writing | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, disaster, time-travel, family
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | romance | family | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
