2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | badminton | skiing | parkour | climbing |

