.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, blueberry, eggplant, mango
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating grapes and the person eating mango##2
3. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
4. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | mango | blueberry | grapes | eggplant |

