.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, disco, ambient, blues
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
4. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | disco | soul | blues |

 